OL,7,FElderly people are losing more than a
OL,8,Fmillion pounds a day due to a rise in
OL,9,Fonline scams, according to new figures.
OL,11,FThe figures, obtained from Action Fraud
OL,12,Funder the Freedom of Information Act,
OL,13,Fcover all fraud cases where the victim
OL,14,Fwas 65 or older.
OL,16,FIt revealed that #1.7bn has been lost
OL,17,Fby over-65s across the UK in the past
OL,18,Ffour years ` meaning that on average
OL,19,Fthe age group is losing about #1.2m to
OL,20,Ffraud each day.
